Right now I have bronze BP, bronze helm, 2 jagged bands, noe earings, rhino leggings with 6AC, and the rest leather.<br>
For weapons I have Bladed Thulian Claws 5/19, PGT 6/26 I think, Enameled Black Mace 8/28, Dragoon Dirk, 6/22, and a Forged Iron Bastard Sword I belive is what it is called 20/40.<br>
I have not used 2hb at all for lack of decent weapon, should I?<br>
All skills are maxed except for that one.  I am a Half-elf so str seems to be a problem, I am currently at 96str at level 17.  I am in Oasis killing crocs or orcs, grouped and sometimes solo.  I have about 450pp to spend on upgrades, I know I need earings, just haven't had the heart to sit through EC and search since I don't know what I am looking for or what price is good.<br>
Thanks for the help.<br>
<br>
Lanolwen, warrior of 17 campaigns. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uroehm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Roehm</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 18<br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/2/01 12:23:22 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Equipment Help</span><hr size=1> Heh better equipment than I had at 17th =P (full banded and duel langsaexs, all those were the days)<br>
<br>
Earrings get a pair of cougar claws or orc fangs.<br>
<br>
Pairs are pretty cheap these days, at 17th I'd go with orc fangs for the extra hps, but to each their own. Remember AC on you ears is good.<br>
<br>
Roehm Ironwolf<br>
57th Mymridon of the Tribunal<br>
