<br>
Gauntlets: 2 star rubies<br>
Bracers: 1 sapphire each<br>
Vambraces 2 fire emeralds<br>
Greaves: 2 star rubies<br>
Helm: 1 ruby<br>
Pauldrun: 1 fire emerald<br>
Boots: 2 sapphires<br>
BP: 3 rubies<br>
<br>
Since you wont be getting all of the pieces at once, you should easily be able to afford it. Any 1 piece should run you 100pp-200pp tops.<br>
<br>
